comments: Valanciunas (NOP) extends his arm into Fox 's(SAC) path on the hand-off and delivers contact.
Jones (NOP) jumps from point A to point B and extends his forearm into Fox's (SAC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Graham (NOP) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) and doesn't affect his ability to drive.
Hart (NOP) jumps vertically and makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) during the driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) does not bring his hand underneath the ball during his drive.
Graham (NOP) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fox (SAC) during the steal, and any contact that occurs after is considered incidental.
After the ball is dislodged, Graham (NOP) makes incidental contact with Holmes (SAC) in the backcourt.
Murphy III (NOP) commits a take foul on Holmes (SAC).
Harkless (SAC) places and extends two hands into Marshall's (NOP) back, which affects his ability to get to the pass.
Murphy III (NOP) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Ingram (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt goes out of bounds.
Ingram (NOP) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Ingram (NOP) receives the pass before he establishes in the front court.
